title: Bosch CBCL1260M 12 In. 60 Tooth Edge Cordless Circular Saw Blade for General Purpose
features: USE WITH: Optimized for any 12" miter saw or slide miter saw
VERSATILITY: Best for fast cross cutting, cutoff and trim of wood and plywood
PRECISION: SpeedCoat antifriction finish for faster and effortless cutting
DURABLE: Blades are designed for tough construction jobs, because they are engineered with Brute Carbide, an upgraded C3/C4 micrograin carbide formulation that increases impact resistance
LONGEVITY: Bosch cordless blades are optimized for cordless cutting, with reduced kerf for speed, less waste, and extended battery life
description: Bosch Edge Circular Saw Blades start sharp, stay sharp and resist impact damage for long life. They are designed for tough construction jobs, because they are engineered with Brute Carbide, an upgraded C3/C4 micrograin carbide formulation that increases impact resistance. They have face-ground teeth for clean cuts and excellent finish. They also feature extra-thin steel plate for less friction that equals more cuts per charge. To avoid warping, these blades have been built with expansion slots. These blades also feature control cut shoulders to reduce kickback, and they have body slots for excessive heat.
